item.title: Thm Room Autopsy
item.description: Autopsy Learn how to use Autopsy to investigate artifacts from a disk image. Use your knowledge to investigate an employee who is being accused of leaking private company data. Profile Support Task 01: Introduction What is Autopsy? The official description: “Autopsy is the premier open source forensics platform which is fast, easy-to-use, and capable of analyzing all types of mobile devices and digital media. Its plug-in architecture enables extensibility from community-developed or custom-built modules.
